<plot>Damian and Mark are two bored 16-year-olds who long to escape their tiny forgotten village high on the Northern moors of England. They spend their time idly taking pot-shots at sheep and passing cars with Damian's air-rifle. Their world changes when they covertly witness a large thug and a business man meet in a deserted lay-by to exchange drugs and money. The drug deal goes horribly wrong and results in the thug killing his "drug dealer" business associate. When the thug urgently flees the scene, the two boys take the opportunity to steal the drug dealer's classic American Cadillac, a case full of cocaine, his gun, and the money. Now all they have to do is; buy a spade to bury the drug dealer's body (stashed in the trunk), appease Damian's mouthy girlfriend, lose their virginity, get off the moors and head South. Easier said than done when the thug is in pursuit and you're - Rebels Without A Clue.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?457496</url></doc>
